        <abstract> 
<p>Agrees to stereotyping <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> [6th ed.].</p>  
<p>Asks that 500 or 1000 more copies of <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi> be printed. Will make no corrections except the number of thousands on title page. Would like to revise [<hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>] if it goes on selling.</p> 
